"Eraser Report V":
"Same request as always, D-arker annihilation.
Your target is Bru Ringarda. I won't ask about
the location. I won't ask about your methods.
Just eliminate your target.

No compassion or hesitation is necessary.
Pile up the bodies
as far as the eye can see.

*Hostiles of Lv.50 or higher"

"いつもの依頼、ダーカー殲滅だ。
目標はブリュー・リンガーダ。
場所は問わない。手段も問わない。
ただ、目標を始末しろ。

躊躇も憐憫も必要ない。
見渡す限り、あいつらの屍を
積み重ねてやれ。

※Lv.50～のエネミーが対象"
